Template: grizzly-network/ip
Type: string
Default: 192.168.1.1
Description: What is this PC's IP address?
 Specify the ipv4 address which this PC will use on its eth0/br0 interface.

Template: grizzly-network/wifi_ap
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Host Grizzly wireless AP?
 Specify whether this PC should provide the Grizzly wireless access point.

Template: grizzly-network/wifi_ssid
Type: string
Default: GRIZZLY
Description: Grizzly access point SSID?
 Specify the SSID to use for the Grizzly wireless access point.

Template: grizzly-network/wifi_password
Type: string
Default: clearpath
Description: Grizzly access point password?
 Specify the password to use for the Grizzly wireless access point.

Template: grizzly-network/gateway_ip
Type: string
Default: 192.168.1.2
Description: Grizzly br0 gateway IP?
 When this machine is not providing the wireless AP, what IP should it look to for a gateway to the internet? This should be the IP of
 the computer providing the NAT and WAN port.
